The soothing sounds of sleepy pigs. 🐖💫 #pigmagic

It was Eunice’s last day. I had hoped she would make it to grass, but this sunny day would do. 

As old as my teenage daughter. My first ewe.  She taught me a lot about shepherding and even more about myself. 

Eunice had many beautiful lambs over the years, and stopped catching a few years back.  Lived out peaceful retirement, getting extra tweats always. 

Her aging accelerated quickly this winter.  And not kindly. 

Today, she had all the best snacks in the sunshine, and in a blink, her time in this world was over. 

I will love her forever. 

#lambmagic
